===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], Yarmouth had a population of 61, with 29 households and 14 families residing in the community. The [[population density]] was 35.6 inhabitants per square mile (13.8/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 36 housing units at an average density of 21.0 per square mile (8.1/km<sup>2</sup>), of which 19.4% were vacant; the homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 100.0%. All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A87330&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 2, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A87330&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 2, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of the 29 households, 13.8% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 34.5% were [[Marriage|married-couple]] households, 3.4% were cohabitating-couple households, 17.2% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 44.8% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. Nonfamily households made up 51.7% of all households. About 44.8% of all households were made up of individuals, and 34.5% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age was 33.8 years. Age distribution was 18.0% under 20, 0.0% from 20 to 24, 44.3% from 25 to 44, 26.2% from 45 to 64, and 11.5% age 65 or older; 16.4% of residents were under age 18. The gender makeup of the community was 55.7% male and 44.3% female. For every 100 females there were 125.9 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 142.9 males.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

